---
title: SuperQuick South Indian-Style Tilapia Curry with Buttery Basmati Rice
description: Take a trip to South India with this super-quick fragrant fish curry made with tilapia! Served with fluffy rice and a dollop of cilantro-spiked yogurt, nothing could be more satisfying.

